      <!-- Section 7: Week-by-Week Prep Plan -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The 4-Week Pre-Tournament Study Plan</h2>

      <p>If your tournament is four weeks away, here is an efficient daily study schedule. Thirty minutes a day is enough — consistency matters more than marathon sessions.</p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Week</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Focus</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Daily Practice</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Goal</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium">1</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Two-letter words</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">20 min flashcards + 10 min testing</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">100% recall of all 127</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium">2</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Q-without-U + high-value shorts</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">15 min word drills + 15 min games</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">No Q panic, consistent J/X/Z plays</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium">3</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Bingo stems + clock practice</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">10 min anagrams + 20 min timed games</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Spot 1 bingo per game, stay under 25 min</td>
            </tr>
